Reactions As Davido Proposes To Chioma. PHOTO: Instagram.com/davidoofficial Nigerian Afro-pop singer David Adeleke popularly known by his stage name, Davido recently proposed to his long time girlfriend Chioma Rowland. Davido proposed to Chioma in London, the United Kingdom on Thursday night, September 12, 2019. The “Blow My Mind” crooner took his girlfriend out on a dinner date in a restaurant in London, where he proposed to her. Davido took to his Instagram page to share a photo of the proposal. “SHE SAID YES!!!! BIG ROCK  #ASSURANCE2020“ “MY SWEET CHUBBY HANDS!! @thechefchi  …..” Davido captioned as he shared a video of the diamond ring on Chioma’s finger:   MY SWEET CHUBBY HANDS!! @thechefchi  ….. A post shared by  Davido Adeleke (@davidoofficial) on Sep 12, 2019 at 3:29pm PDT  Chioma also shared a photo from the proposal on her Instagram page with the caption: “🥺🥰 I love you @davidoofficial (You didn’t even let me wax yet )” The proposal is coming a week after the couple had their an introduction ceremony in Lagos, Nigeria. Davido and Chioma have one of the most adored relationships in Nigeria and here are some of the reactions to the news of the engagement, some of which range from praises to funny: Labelmate, Peruzzi shared a video of the Davido as he knelt to ask Chioma’s hand in marriage:         The couple is set to have their wedding ceremony in 2020.